      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span><br>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/56a7afb2342c71f6d852a1470599e4e6_1497849836373263518.png",
                "id": "talent15801",
                "key": "Parthian Shot",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Parthian Shot"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>. Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Menifest Gale</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Manifest Gale</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh melancarkan Charge Attack:</span> mengonsumsi 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Elemen Tidak Selaras</span> lebih sedikit dan <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkan diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> dan memberikan status <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Pressurized Collapse</span> kepada Karakter target.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/6f3f1e66aac8d91ecca768d4a7f48e56_3572885993746643505.png",
                "id": "talent71700",
                "key": "Wind Realm of Nasamjnin",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Wind Realm of Nasamjnin"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> dan memanggil <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Dazzling Polyhedron</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/bec3c6e3c0067cc3e0340d50df63f27e_2884623475340991886.png",
                "id": "talent60203",
                "key": "The Wind's Secret Ways",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "anemo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "The Wind's Secret Ways"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengabatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 3</span> </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat panggilan ini berada dalam arena:</span> <span style=\"color: #80FFD7\">Anemo DMG</span> yang diterima Karakter lawan +1.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8489890348981811393.png",
                "id": "talent41650",
                "key": "Dazzling Polyhedron",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/7c29f5ce38f0d332fbd3113f1b605a5c_656156027223246921.png",
                "title": "Dazzling Polyhedron"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Cryo DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Hydro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Pyro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 255, 215)\">Anemo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Swirl</span>: Mengakibatkan 1 poin Electro DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/c97292d96456bfe4abeca16bfce801e4_1345510757814570744.png",
                "id": "talent15253",
                "key": "Anemo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Anemo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Charged Attack</span></strong></p><p>Jika total Dadu Elemental berjumlah genap sebelum Aksi Tempur giliranmu dimulai, maka Normal Attack yang digunakan akan dianggap sebagai Charged Attack.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Elemen Tidak Selaras</span></strong></p><p>Kamu dapat menggunakan Dadu Elemental apa pun untuk membayar jenis biaya ini.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Pressurized Collapse</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">:</span> Karakter yang terpengaruh akan menjadi \"Karakter aktif\".</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 1</span></p><p>(Maksimum satu status di sisi yang sama)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/05/06/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_7351547209174931046.png",
                "id": "talent17028",
